{"tid":1876283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"首完全體唱新歌 Mina回歸TWICE登推特趨勢榜冠軍","createTime":"2020-02-12T09:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T09:56:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"faf43ffa9507c8502e59afef173c507b0eacdd79","tid":1876283,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T09:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PN9a07iwh4lEwc9we5IkFQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/3897967d041bd35791aded246c3100f1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPN9a07iwh4lEwc9we5IkFQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2F3897967d041bd35791aded246c3100f1&h=4cfc5df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國大勢女團TWICE昨（11日）在日本福岡舉行《TWICE WORLD TOUR 2019 「TWICELIGHTS」IN JAPAN》演唱會，日籍成員Mina（名井南）現身舞台，與其他8名成員一起表演〈Feel Special〉，這也是這首歌第一次由TWICE完全體帶來的表演，讓歌迷興奮又激動，從頭尖叫到結束。<br />\n<br />\nMina經醫師診斷出嚴重恐慌焦慮症，自去年8月全面暫停活動，在10月的TWICE出道4週年見面會曾短暫露面，直到昨日才重新站上舞台，與TWICE成員合體表演〈Feel Special〉，歌迷在Mina唱歌時給予最大聲的尖叫，歡迎她歸隊。而Mina也向粉絲問候：「我是Mina，今天請大家多多指教。」<br />\n<br />\nTWICE官方推特在演唱會進行期間，即立刻公開了Mina表演的影片，讓未能到現場欣賞演唱會的海內外粉絲第一時間接收Mina歸隊訊息，而TWICE的YouTube官方頻道也上傳了9人完全體表演的〈Feel Special〉影片，為了慶祝這個好消息，TWICE粉絲紛紛以「#ProudOfYouMina」關鍵字在推特刷文，立刻登上了推特的世界趨勢榜冠軍。"},{"pid":"c32c563a2c547028ca8fab482c0e8eead3dbebd6","tid":1876283,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/3ac7695b88c725349b245b02ac7bfbe1/01ce6ff0cbd3bde8-7c/s250x400/60b96c24e1bc4a1d6e74b861b344cde78b074f7d.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F3ac7695b88c725349b245b02ac7bfbe1%2F01ce6ff0cbd3bde8-7c%2Fs250x400%2F60b96c24e1bc4a1d6e74b861b344cde78b074f7d.gifv&h=039c1b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/4e30b65668c637bf